bugs
----

features
--------

- keyboard+drag to quickly add
  - rectangles

- UI
  - verb/cancel dialogs
  - toolbar/palette for setting things on the right side of page

- selection
  - drag event to draw a <div>, get its bounds, work out what intersects it

- mousewheel to scroll

- editors
- undo!

- alignment functions
- alignment guides
- inset guides

- shapes
  - tabs
  - rectangle
  - horizontal rule
  - text label
  - text paragraph
  - various icons
  - icon and label
  - combobox
  - button
  - tables
  - fancy arrows

- colour palette
  - black
  - white
  - 4 greys
  - blue
  - red
  - green
  - amber
  - orange

- text parsing e.g. this is *bold*
- resizing
- export to GIF

